# 🥋 Jiu-Jitsu Log

> A minimalist Android app for tracking Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu training sessions. Built with Kotlin/Jetpack Compose.

---

## ✨ Features

- Log sessions with:
  - 📅 Date
  - 🥋 Class Type (Gi / No-Gi)
  - 🔁 Rounds + Submissions
  - 📌 Positional Focus
  - 📝 Notes & Reflections
- View sessions in **chronological order**
- Light/Dark Theme toggle
- Persistent data storage using **Room**
- Shared preferences for default values
- "Are you sure?" delete confirmation

---

## 🧰 How to Run

1. Clone the repo:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/jiu-jitsu-log.git
   cd jiu-jitsu-log
